snippet.title: Cookie Run Season 4 Promo Video
snippet.description:
Season 4 is here!

1. New Breakout Episode: Sands of Yogurca
Choose a path with the new crossroads feature!

2. Meet Yogurt Cream Cookie
Slide to choose & summon a magical spirit!

3. Meet Magic Lamp
Creates Yogurt Star Jellies & collects missed Jellies.

4. Fabled Magic Carpet
Flies away & returns with precious Jellies.

5. Daily Quests Reworked
Cinnamon Cookie has worked his magic on the Daily Quests system!

6. Treasure Hunt
Complete the missions and earn Treasures!
